725638f-a.title: Queens: 75th Place - Formanville Avenue
725638f-a.text:
Corner of 75th Place and Formanville Avenue, as seen
fros a dump, uueens.
P. L. Sperr, photographer
July 1, 1940
Neg. No. A-1079

726739f-b.title: Queens: Furmanville Avenue - 75th Street
726739f-b.text:
Furmanville Ave. (formerly Juniper Swamp Road), north side, east
from 75th Street, showing the J. Bedell House from 1852-1860, in the
foreground. The Sickman family were owners from 1873 to 1891.
May 1923.
View 2: March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
